The '''Imperial Academy of Science and Methodology''' was an academy which taught science to [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] citizens.<ref name="journal7">{{JournalCite|7|Old Corellian: A Guide for the Curious Scholar}}</ref>

Among the researchers at the academy were the [[Issori]] scholar [[Arner Figgis]], who held a prestigious tenure at the academy before leaving for unknown reasons,<ref name="journal7" /> and [[Chief Scientist/Legends|Chief Scientist]] [[K'ar Zah]].<ref name="SWG:SCoS">{{SWGcite|exp=AED|type=terminal||Serve Cause of Science}}</ref>

